description:
 Alpha brainwaves are excellent for engaging the mind. When we are consuming knowledge, our mind operates in a predominantly alpha brainwave. This meditation uses the alpha brainwave tuned to 13.82687 cycles per second.

Tapping into the third eye chakra, this meditation tunes itself to this chakra. This results in a meditation that can engage the mind and sharpen our attention to the subject at hand.

In our society, consuming enormous amounts of information has become a requirement. This meditation has been designed to assist people in consuming these large amounts of data.

Suggested Use: Can be used for deep focus on subject matter that requires memory. Can also be used during work to enhance focus of daily activities. 

